      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior has significant body damage, including deep scratches, several large dents, and visible rust patches on the wheel arches. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul, the transmission slips under load, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for spare parts.",
