    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is a fantastic option for anyone seeking dependable transportation on a budget! It's in fair condition, showing some honest cosmetic wear and tear, but it remains a solid performer on the road. Perfect for a first car or a sturdy daily commuter!",
