      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary motorcar, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that reflects meticulous stewardship. Every aspect of this automobile has been preserved to the highest standard, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. For the discerning individual seeking a vehicle of peerless quality and mechanical integrity, this offering stands without equal.",
      "price": 48500.0,
